{"tid":1744904,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[極重要求入] 維護區議會選舉公正宣言","createTime":"2019-11-22T03:26:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T03:22:39.000Z","uid":275872,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c602b7adf3bc0e7ec5d51f9b4b24e6df1094573a","tid":1744904,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:26:00.000Z","msg":"建制人士已經放晒風，話驚D暴徒會破壞票站，令<span style=\"color: red;\">投票腰斬</span>，想要一個公平公正既選舉。<br />\n<br />\n我知道連登仔都係守法好公民，所以我希望大家可以同我一齊，嚴正<span style=\"color: red;\">向全世界宣佈</span>：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">本人宣佈，對香港選舉制度及香港人充滿信心，不需要亦不會阻人投票、騷擾投票人或票站人員、破壞票站或作出其他有可能破壞區議會選舉進行或影響其公平性的行為。本人亦會在能力範圍內致力阻止任何人作出破壞區議會選舉順利進行的行為，包括但不止於報警、向選舉主任投訴、在情況許可下對該人士行使公民拒捕權，以維護選舉制度的尊嚴。謹此宣告。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講定先，投票日邊個搞事，就要受到應有既制裁同報應。<br />\n今次真係好重要，求文宣。<br />\n<br />\n正評即係一齊宣告!!<br />\n求正評，求推到選舉日 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: blue;\"></span>"},{"pid":"5c2452ea97cff3e6c2d11cd9d7dd2ae150766e95","tid":1744904,"uid":43278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:26:56.000Z","msg":"正皮！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d3b94a0348cc9afc46946ebb8ce2c5583779a0","tid":1744904,"uid":43278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:27:34.000Z","msg":"即使未必會贏都要投票<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03e8857df948e190edc7661184ed298c3f3b7740","tid":1744904,"uid":275872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T03:28:47.000Z","msg":"無錯!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wai